<doc id="296" url="https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki?curid=296" title="Agawam">
<h1>Agawam</h1>
&lt;templatestyles src="Pagebanner/styles.css"/&gt;
♡❤♡Agawam♡❤♡ is a town in the &lt;a href="Hampden%20County"&gt;Hampden County&lt;/a&gt; part of the &lt;a href="Pioneer%20Valley"&gt;Pioneer Valley&lt;/a&gt; region of &lt;a href="Massachusetts"&gt;Massachusetts&lt;/a&gt;. It includes the village of Feeding Hills.

<h2>Get in</h2>

♡❤♡By car♡❤♡

U.S. Route 5 runs along the eastern border of Agawam along the Connecticut River. It connects to &lt;a href="Suffield%20%28Connecticut%29"&gt;Suffield&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Connecticut"&gt;Connecticut&lt;/a&gt; in the south and &lt;a href="West%20Springfield%20%28Massachusetts%29"&gt;West Springfield&lt;/a&gt; in the north. State Route 57 is the major east/west route through the city.

<h2>Get around</h2>

<h2>See</h2>

<h2>Do</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q846548"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Six Flags New England♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;1623 Main St&lt;/bdi&gt;, toll-free: &lt;bdi class="tel listing-tollfree"&gt; +1-877-474-9352 &lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The largest theme park in New England with ten roller-coasters, numerous thrill rides, and an expansive water park for those sweltering summer days. It opens in April as the weather starts to get warm and closes in November as it starts to get cold.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;span class="listing-sister-icons"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q1646912"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Robinson State Park♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;North Street&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +1 413 786-2877 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;State Park located on the Westfield River. Picnicking, mountain biking, hiking, walking, swimming.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;span class="listing-sister-icons"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;

</ul>
<h2>Buy</h2>

<h2>Eat</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡The 911♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The 911 is a tiny little "hole-in-the-wall" restaurant on the corner of North West Street and North Westfield Street. Despite its small size and out-of-the-way location, The 911 has the best burgers and hot dogs in all of Agawam, possibly in the entire Pioneer Valley. The menu isn't much more complicated than that, but the food that they do have is outstanding.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;

</ul>
