BULLET::::- ♡❤♡&lt;a href="http%3A//www.alpacafest.org"&gt;Annual Michigan International Alpacafest&lt;/a&gt;♡❤♡ — Held every year in &lt;a href="Michigan"&gt;Michigan&lt;/a&gt;.

