<h3>Africa</h3>

<h2>Stay safe</h2>

During a visit to a working farm or ranch, you will most likely encounter farm equipment and animals. Supervise your children around both and encourage them to use some restraint. Any visit to a rural area may include mud and manure, so wear boots or old sneakers. Beware of &lt;a href="pests"&gt;pests&lt;/a&gt;.

