BULLET::::- ♡❤♡Centro Comericial Espacio♡❤♡ opened in April 2015, is a mall located in the eastern part of th city, includes a cinema complex, food court and stores like Office Depot and Soriana supermarket. It sits right beside the Ojo Caliente spa.

</ul>
