The main Apollo Hospital is in the twin city of &lt;a href="Gandhinagar"&gt;Gandhinagar&lt;/a&gt;, but very close to the airport. The Apollo City Centre is in Ellisbridge area (&lt;a href="Ahmedabad/West%20Zone"&gt;West Zone&lt;/a&gt;).

