♡❤♡Ainu♡❤♡ (アイヌ・イタㇰ, ♡❤Aynu=itak♡❤) is one of the ethnic languages of &lt;a href="Hokkaido"&gt;Hokkaido&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Japan"&gt;Japan&lt;/a&gt;.

<h2>Pronunciation guide</h2>

