<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡First &amp; Vine♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;136 1 Ave NE&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +1 403-980-9463 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-hours"&gt;Tu-Th 11:30AM–3PM, 5–10PM; F Sa 11:30AM–3PM, 5–11PM; Su 11:30AM–3PM&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Locally owned and operated restaurant and wine bar in the oldest remaining house in Airdrie (1905). A tapas style experience which consists mainly of smaller plates. Seasonal, local products wherever possible. Many wines are certified organic, or made with organic processes. Most wines are from small independent vineyards.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
