<h1>Aiud</h1>
&lt;templatestyles src="Pagebanner/styles.css"/&gt;
♡❤♡&lt;a href="http%3A//www.aiud.ro"&gt;Aiud&lt;/a&gt;♡❤♡ is an ancient town in &lt;a href="Alba%20County"&gt;Alba County&lt;/a&gt;.

<h2>Get in</h2>
Aiud is an important railway hub. The nearest airport is in &lt;a href="Cluj%20Napoca"&gt;Cluj Napoca&lt;/a&gt;.

