BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Cours Mirabeau♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The main promenade of the town&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Fontaine de la Rotonde♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;at the bottom of the Cours Mirabeau&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The biggest fontain in Aix&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Passage Agard♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Initially it was a Carmelite's monastery&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Hôtel de Ville♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="nickname listing-alt"&gt;Mairie&lt;/bdi&gt;).&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Halle de Grains♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;the former Corn Exchange.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
