BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q1025950"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Filitosa♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;20 south of Ajaccio off highway T40&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-hours"&gt;April-Oct 09:00 to sunset&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Prehistoric (mostly Bronze Age) settlement with standing stones and small museum. Easiest visited from Ajaccio, but also an easy day-trip from Bonifacio or Porto Vecchio. Other notable standing stones in the area are at Palaggiu and Stanfari.&lt;/bdi&gt; &lt;bdi class="note listing-price"&gt;&lt;abbr title=" €7 ≈ US$, JP¥, £"&gt;€7&lt;/abbr&gt; , children under 8 free&lt;/bdi&gt;.&lt;span class="listing-sister-icons"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;

