BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q2581206"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Tusenfryd Amusement park♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Fryds vei 25&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Vinterbro, &lt;a href="%C3%85s"&gt;Ås&lt;/a&gt;
</ul>
